 202354                    result = result < 0 ? -1 : result > 0 ? 1 : 0;
 202355                    return true;
 2356                }
 02357                if (TryCompare(y, x, out result)) {
 02358                    result = result > 0 ? -1 : result < 0 ? 1 : 0;
 02359                    return true;
 2360                }
 2361
 02362                if (!stringCompare) {
 02363                    result = -1;
 02364                    return false;
 2365                }
 2366
 2367                // Compare stringified version
 02368                var s1 = x?.ToString() ?? "null";
 02369                var s2 = y?.ToString() ?? "null";
 02370                result = s1.CompareTo(s2);
 02371                return true;
 2372            }
 2373
 2374            /// <summary>
 2375            /// Compare
 2376            /// </summary>
 2377            /// <param name="x"></param>
 2378            /// <param name="y"></param>
 2379            /// <param name="result"></param>
 2380            /// <returns></returns>
 2381            private static bool TryCompare(object x, object y, out int result) {
 202382                if (x is IComparable cv1) {
 2383                    try {
 202384                        if (x.GetType() != y.GetType()) {
 02385                            if (y is IConvertible c) {
 02386                                y = c.ToType(x.GetType(), CultureInfo.InvariantCulture);
 2387                            }
 2388                        }
 202389                        result = cv1.CompareTo(y);
 202390                        return true;
 2391                    }
 02392                    catch {
 02393                    }
 2394                }
 02395                result = -1;
 02396                return false;
 202397            }
 2398        }

 02879                    if (!TryGetValue(out var o)) {
 02880                        o = GetRawValue();
 2881                    }
 02882                    if (o is byte[] b) {
 02883                        o = Convert.ToBase64String(b);
 2884                    }
 02885                    hc.Add(o);
 02886                    break;
 2887                case VariantValueType.Values:
 02888                    foreach (var value in GetArrayElements()) {
 02889                        value.GetDeepHashCode(ref hc);
 2890                    }
 2891                    break;
 2892                case VariantValueType.Object:
 02893                    var p2 = PropertyNames.OrderBy(k => k);
 02894                    foreach (var k in p2) {
 02895                        hc.Add(k);
 02896                        this[k].GetDeepHashCode(ref hc);
 2897                    }
 2898                    break;
 2899                default:
 02900                    hc.Add(GetRawValue());
 2901                    break;
 2902            }
 02903        }
